				<wikidot:authorName>ProcyonLotor</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>778357</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>It very much seems like this exists just to have a defenestration skip rather than being born of any legitimate idea beyond &quot;lol defenestration&quot;. Which I'm sure is how a lot of articles are born but it seems particularly glaring here. It's too competent to downvote but I can't upvote in good faith.</p> <p>Also, if I'm not mistaken, the Junius pamphlet was Rosa Luxemburg, not Lenin.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
