					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-8045816#post-4025077</guid>
				<title>When God Closes A Door, He Throws Something Out A Window</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-8045816/scp-4034#post-4025077</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 15 Oct 2018 17:38:12 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Captain Kirby</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3440103</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>It's done. We finally have a defenestration skip. They said it couldn't be done. Or rather that it shouldn't be done&#8230; but we did it anyway goddamn it.</p> <p>I'd like to give a huge thank you to my coauthor: Modern_Erasmus, who looked at my original concept for my defenestration skip, and essentially said &quot;this is bad, let me help you make it better&quot;. Also he was the one who pushed me to make this more of a historical skip too which was definitely the right move. So three hurrahs for him!</p> <p>I'd also like to thank my critiquers: Conwell, HumidHermit, AKFrost, Meserach, magnadeus, and Eskobar</p> <p>Happy defenestrating!</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
